      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "content: '# Web Document\n\n\n  ## Metadata\n\n\n  - title: How do I submit an accessible ticket request?\n\n  - url: https://axssupportanz.axs.com/hc/en-au/articles/25569859097884-How-do-I-submit-an-accessible-ticket-request\n\n  - source: AXS Help Centre ANZ\n\n  - domain: axssupportanz.axs.com\n\n\n  ## Content\n\n\n  # How do I submit an accessible ticket request?\n\n\n  Customers who need accessible seating or have specific access needs can make a request\n  through the AXS Helpdesk.\n\n\n  ## To submit a request\n\n\n  1. Go to the AXS Helpdesk: https://axssupportanz.axs.com/hc/en-au/requests/new\n\n  2. Select the venue the enquiry concerns.\n\n  3. Choose **Accessibility Requirement** from the dropdown menu.\n\n  4. Complete the request form and submit it.\n\n\n  After submission, the AXS team reviews the request and responds with the next steps.\n\n\n  ## Customer Support Opening Hours\n\n\n  Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm (AEST).\n\n\n  Saturday and Sunday: closed.\n\n  '\nmetadata: {}\ntitle: How do I submit an accessible ticket request?\nurl: https://axssupportanz.axs.com/hc/en-au/articles/25569859097884-How-do-I-submit-an-accessible-ticket-request"
